{
  "text": "After the veil, in our particular case now, we have in the circuitry of which we were speaking a what you call a blockage that first occurs an orange ray. Could you describe what occurs with this first blockage and what its effects are on each of the entities, assuming that one blocks and the other does not, or if both are blocked. I am wrong. This material has been covered previously. If both entities are blocked, both will have an increased hunger for the same activity, seeking to unblock the baffled flow of energy. If one entity is blocked and the other vibrates in love. A dew, a two, an impression that this entity might approve helpful in this endeavor. The green array, active individual, shall polarize slightly in the direction of a service to others, but have only the energy with which it began.",
